      "type": "text",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 208,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 20,
      "text": "❌ Keep at Origin",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "noEdgeBody",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 232,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 132,
      "text": "🗄️ DB queries (no DB access at edge)\n\n⚙️ Complex business logic\n   (payments, ML inference, etc)\n\n📁 File system access\n\n🔄 Long-running processes\n   (edge has ~50ms CPU budget)\n\n📦 Large dependencies\n   (edge has ~1MB bundle limit)\n\nEdge KV (Cloudflare KV) works\nfor simple key-value reads only",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
